{"title":"飞向宇宙的歌声","authors":["商泽军"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向宇宙的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀揣着太空发来的邀请"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举着通向宇宙的签证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在五千年梦想的发射塔上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的载人飞船傲然腾空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论是什么样的肤色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论讲的是什么语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的内心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有一个梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从大地上腾飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去漫步遨游太空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们想和蓝色的星星对话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以在上面种植庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以走亲戚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们想地球人的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对方一定能听懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有了各种各样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是就有了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天看来可笑的举动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人把鸟的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绑在身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的坐土火箭旅行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在风中奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的手中牵着层层的风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是世间没有了飞天遨游的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会觉得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个大地少了嫦娥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮也会减去风情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是世间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有了飞天遨游的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎会张大眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指点夜幕上的星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果世间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有了飞翔的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类就会像蠢笨的动物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匍匐在自然的巨掌下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏睡不醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果世间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有了飞翔的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天会减去色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河流没有了歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广漠的太空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是寂寞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太空也盼望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳绿花红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太空也想有朋友的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那寂寞的嫦娥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把长长的舞袖已准备好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她想听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自故乡的和声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那吴刚呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他准备好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把最新配制的桂花酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧给遥远的宾朋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都是可以突破的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都是可以交流的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球与星斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人和白人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们需要突破的界限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是山河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要突破的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是自己的头脑和思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从刀耕火种中走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走向工业革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从原子走向太空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们穿越历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从诗经到唐诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从唐诗到宋词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们突破的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一切的桎梏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的地平线在地球的外面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们地平线是运动的呼声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实践把我们提高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在实践中验证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从匍匐到奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从暗夜到光明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和星球是孪生的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都从宇宙的母腹诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到太空去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们去寻找新的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新的生命里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们知道了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了多少血与火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了多少的坎坷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们造出了自己的飞船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像诺亚方舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个船上满载的是希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的神舟飞船上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是希望的产床"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个民族的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始诞生，开始有了生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许我们经历了太多的坎坷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许我们经历了太多的苦痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当飞船上天的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是在童话和传说中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许我的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有被磨难打磨的千疮百孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当飞船上天的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的眼泪开始飞迸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们说喜极而泣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想这样的泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满含幸福、激动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有民族的委屈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我身上的留影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的屈辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太空中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂立着中华民族的光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是飞天的子孙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才迈开了第一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还要到月球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还要会见火星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会布满整个太空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会铭记着这个日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有五千年飞天梦的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公元2003年的10月15日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们挣脱了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地的羁绊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们飞上了太空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去一个风景地旅行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正因为我们有了梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才有了民族的寻梦远行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从屈原的问天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后羿的遗憾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从敦煌的壁画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到卫星的上天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到今天的神舟飞船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们证明了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们无愧飞天的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们能把梦境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用实力证明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天的梦给了我们智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天的梦给了我们想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天的梦给了我们热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们唱给宇宙的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让历史铭记这一刻吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铭记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们飞向宇宙的歌声！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}